 towns and sister  cities in Argentina}}\nMendoza is [[Twin towns and sister cities|twinned]]  with:\n*{{flagicon|BRA}} [[S\u00e3o Paulo]], Brazil<ref name=\"S\u00e3o Paulo twinnings\">{{cite web|url=http://www3.prefeitura.sp.gov.br/cadlem/secretarias/negocios_juridicos/cadlem/integra.asp?alt=11072007L%20144710000|title = Pesquisa de Legisla\u00e7\u00e3o Municipal \u2013 No 14471|accessdate=2013-08-23|work=Prefeitura da Cidade de S\u00e3o Paulo [Municipality of the City of S\u00e3o Paulo]|language=Portuguese|trans-title=Research Municipal Legislation \u2013 No 14471|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111018123138/http://www3.prefeitura.sp.gov.br/cadlem/secretarias/negocios_juridicos/cadlem/integra.asp?alt=11072007L%20144710000|archivedate = 2011-10-18}}</ref><ref name=\"S\u00e3o Paulo WikiSource\">[http://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Lei_Municipal_de_S%C3%A3o_Paulo_14471_de_2007 Lei Municipal de S\u00e3o Paulo 14471 de 2007] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928023927/http://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Lei_Municipal_de_S%C3%A3o_Paulo_14471_de_2007 |date=2013-09-28 }} WikiSource {{in lang|pt}}</ref>\n*{{flagicon|BRA}}  [[Sert\u00e3ozinho]], Brazil {{citation needed|date=October 2014}}\n*  {{flagicon|ISR}} [[Ramat Gan]], Israel {{citation needed|date=October 2014}}\n*{{flagicon|MEX}}  [[Monterrey]], Mexico {{citation needed|date=October 2014}}\n*{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Bergamo]], Italy {{citation needed|date=October 2014}}\n*{{flagicon|USA}} [[Miami-Dade County, Florida|Miami-Dade County]], US{{citation needed|date=October 2014}}\n*{{flagicon|USA}}  [[Nashville, Tennessee|Nashville]], US<ref name=\"Nashville sisters\">{{cite web |url=http://www.scnashville.org/ |title=Sister Cities of Nashville |work=SCNashville.org |accessdate=August 3, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110728004357/http://www.scnashville.org/ |archive-date=July 28, 2011 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n* [[1985 Mendoza earthquake]]\n* [[2006 Mendoza earthquake]]\n\n==